xed-Height Slider</b>\n                                    </h5>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                        Click on the image to edit slides.</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div><div class=\"carousel-item slider-image item\">\n                            <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                                <img class=\"d-block w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/grasshopperfundamentosdecodificaciniicertificate-1-1900x1344.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"11\" data-bs-slide-to=\"11\">\n                                <div class=\"carousel-caption d-none d-md-block\" mbr-if=\"showCaption || showText\">\n                                    <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showCaption\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                                        <b>Fixed-Height Slider</b>\n                                    </h5>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                        Click on the image to edit slides.</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div><div class=\"carousel-item slider-image item\">\n                            <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                                <img class=\"d-block w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/grasshopperfundamentosdelacodificacincertificate-1-1900x1344.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"12\" data-bs-slide-to=\"12\">\n                                <div class=\"carousel-caption d-none d-md-block\" mbr-if=\"showCaption || showText\">\n                                    <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showCaption\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                                        <b>Fixed-Height Slider</b>\n                                    </h5>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                        Click on the image to edit slides.</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div><div class=\"carousel-item slider-image item\">\n                            <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                                <img class=\"d-block w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/grasshopperintroduccinalasentrevistascertificate-1-1900x1344.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"13\" data-bs-slide-to=\"13\">\n                                <div class=\"carousel-caption d-none d-md-block\" mbr-if=\"showCaption || showText\">\n                                    <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showCaption\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                                        <b>Fixed-Height Slider</b>\n                                    </h5>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                        Click on the image to edit slides.</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div><div class=\"carousel-item slider-image item\">\n                            <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                                <img class=\"d-block w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/grasshopperintroduccinapginaswebcertificate-1-1900x1344.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"14\" data-bs-slide-to=\"14\">\n                                <div class=\"carousel-caption d-none d-md-block\" mbr-if=\"showCaption || showText\">\n                                    <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showCaption\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                                        <b>Fixed-Height Slider</b>\n                                    </h5>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                        Click on the image to edit slides.</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div><div class=\"carousel-item slider-image item\">\n                            <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                                <img class=\"d-block w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/grasshoppermtodosdearreglocertificate-1-1900x1344.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"15\" data-bs-slide-to=\"15\">\n                                <div class=\"carousel-caption d-none d-md-block\" mbr-if=\"showCaption || showText\">\n                                    <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showCaption\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                                        <b>Fixed-Height Slider</b>\n                                    </h5>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                        Click on the image to edit slides.</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div><div class=\"carousel-item slider-image item\">\n                            <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                                <img class=\"d-block w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/grasshopperusaruneditordecdigocertificate-1-1900x1344.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"16\" data-bs-slide-to=\"16\">\n                                <div class=\"carousel-caption d-none d-md-block\" mbr-if=\"showCaption || showText\">\n                                    <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showCaption\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                                        <b>Fixed-Height Slider</b>\n                                    </h5>\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                        Click on the image to edit slides.</p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        \n                        \n                    </div>\n                    <a class=\"carousel-control carousel-control-prev\" href=\"#{{sliderId}}\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"prev\" data-bs-slide=\"prev\">\n                        <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-arrow-prev\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n                        <span class=\"sr-only visually-hidden\">Previous</span>\n                    </a>\n                    <a class=\"carousel-control carousel-control-next\" href=\"#{{sliderId}}\" role=\"button\" data-slide=\"next\" data-bs-slide=\"next\">\n                        <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-arrow-next\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n                        <span class=\"sr-only visually-hidden\">Next</span>\n                    </a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "tGP9FNAB0o",
          "_anchor": "slider2-d",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "& when not (@fullScreen)": {
              "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
              "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)"
            },
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            ".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn": {
              "color": "#232323"
            },
            ".mbr-text, .mbr-section-title": {
              "@media (max-width: 991px)": {
                "text-align": "center"
              }
            },
            "a.btn": {
              "height": "100%",
              "margin": "0"
            },
            ".mbr-section-btn": {
              "display": "flex",
              "margin-bottom": "1.2rem",
              "width": "100%",
              ".btn": {
                "width": "100%"
              }
            },
            "@media (max-width: 991px)": {
              ".image-wrapper": {
                "margin-bottom": "2rem"
              },
              ".content-wrapper": {
                "flex-direction": "column-reverse"
              }
            },
            ".justify-content-center": {
              "align-items": "center"
            },
            "H1": {
              "color": "#47b5ed"
            }
          },
          "_name": "form4",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"form4\" group=\"Forms\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" plugins=\"formstyler, datepicker\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" name=\"bgColor\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffe885\" selected>\n    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"usedRecaptcha\" value=\"false\"></mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row content-wrapper justify-content-center\">\n            <div mbr-form class=\"col-lg-4 offset-lg-1 mbr-form\">\n<!--Formbuilder Form-->\n<form action=\"franzgmuller999@gmail.com\" name=\"Form Name\" method=\"POST\" class=\"mbr-form form-with-styler\" data-verified=\"franzgmuller999@gmail.com\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div hidden=\"hidden\" data-form-alert class=\"alert alert-success col-12\">Gracias por Escribirme, muy pronto tendrás mi respuesta!</div>\n<div hidden=\"hidden\" data-form-alert-danger class=\"alert alert-danger col-12\">Oops...! some problem!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"dragArea row\">\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12\">\n<h1 mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" class=\"mbr-section-title mb-4\"><b>Escríbeme</b></h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12\">\n<p mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\"> Escríbeme te responderé muy pronto.</p>\n</div>\n<div data-for=\"name\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md col-12 form-group mb-3\">\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Nombre\" data-form-field=\"name\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"form-control\" value>\n</div>\n<div data-for=\"email\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md col-12 form-group mb-3\">\n<input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Correo\" data-form-field=\"email\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"form-control\" value>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 form-group\" data-for=\"textarea\">\n<textarea name=\"textarea\" placeholder=\"Tu Mensaje\" data-form-field=\"textarea\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"form-control\"></textarea>\n</div>\n<div mbr-buttons=\"true\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrLink,-mbrBtnRemove,-mbrBtnAdd\" class=\"col-12 col-md-auto mbr-section-btn\"><a type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-info\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Escribe!</a></div>\n</div>\n</form><!--Formbuilder Form-->\n</div>\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6 offset-lg-1 col-12\">\n                <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                    <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/franz-george-muller-rueda.png\" alt=\"FRANZ GEORGE MULLER RUEDA\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
